GLUE   BASIC   TEMPLATES (1.0)

   LLIMP(N L R) = (N ANT) = L
	  (N CONS) = R.

   LLATOM(N L T) = (N RESOURCE) = L
	  (N TYPE) = T.

    LLQUANT(N B) = (N BINDER) = B.

   LLCLOSURE(G) = G $ (g::* GLUE).

   GLUE-MEANING(R M) =
	  (R MEANING) = M.

  NOSCOPE(G) = (G NOSCOPE) = +.


